  "firstAcquaintance": "A shrewd human woman, she is your capable secretary who manages nearly everything for you.",
  "personality": "Mature and composed, she manages the guildhall with perfect organization, making it seem as though nothing could ever stump her.",
  "like": "None",
  "familiarData": "Lui Rin -- the name is actually a codename, \"610.\"\nLui Rin was born at a lamia ranch. She escaped during a resistance army raid, which led her to join the resistance and learn from them. After the resistance fell, she drifted among several wanderer groups, sometimes disguising herself as a slave to enter towns.\nHer experience with the resistance gave her outstanding planning and coordination abilities. Any task assigned to her can be completed flawlessly. She is a key driving force behind the reborn resistance army, the Hand of Freedom, and serves as the master's important strategist, working together to build the strength to oppose the demon race and step by step make the vision of humanity's resistance a reality.\nBeneath her clothes, Lui Rin's body is covered in scars. She dislikes exposing her skin and does not want to reveal her past.",
